#Shopify Sales & Customer Funnel Analysis

#Overview
This project is a Power BI dashboard built to analyze Shopify sales data and uncover insights related to revenue, customer behavior, and retention.

#Objective
- Analyze sales performance
- Understand customer purchase patterns
- Measure retention and customer lifetime value
- Enable data-driven decision-making

#Tools Used
- Power BI
- DAX
- Data Cleaning & Modeling

#Key KPIs
- Net Sales
- Total Quantity
- Average Order Value
- Total Customers
- Repeat Customers
- Customer Lifetime Value
- Repeat Rate
- Purchase Frequency

#Dashboard Features
- Sales trend over time
- Regional analysis (Map visualization)
- Customer behavior insights
- Payment gateway analysis
- Product category performance
- Drill-through detailed data view

#Key Insights
- Identified top-performing cities and regions
- Repeat customers contribute significantly to revenue
- Certain product categories drive higher sales
- Sales trends reveal peak activity periods

#Files Included
- Power BI Dashboard (.pbix)
- Dataset
- Project Documentation
- Screenshots

#Conclusion
This dashboard helps businesses monitor performance, understand customers, and improve strategic decision-making.
